&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>트랜스포머의 인코더와 디코더 &lt;a href="https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/disk/#%ed%8a%b8%eb%9e%9c%ec%8a%a4%ed%8f%ac%eb%a8%b8%ec%9d%98-%ec%9d%b8%ec%bd%94%eb%8d%94%ec%99%80-%eb%94%94%ec%bd%94%eb%8d%94">&amp;raquo;&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
